sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Platform as Platform Ingress<br/>(Route/Gateway)<br/>TLS Termination
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Endpoint<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant VectorDB as Vector DB<br/>(Milvus/pgvector/Qdrant)
    participant FMS as TrustyAI FMS<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Cloud as Cloud Inference<br/>(Bedrock/WatsonX/Azure)

    Note over Client,Cloud: Flow 1: Client Inference Request via vLLM

    Client->>Platform: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Platform Auth
    Platform->>LlamaStack: Forward Request<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (plaintext)
    LlamaStack->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: API Token (VLLM_API_TOKEN)
    vLLM-->>LlamaStack: Chat Completion Response
    LlamaStack->>PG: Store inference state<br/>SQL 5432/TCP<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PG-->>LlamaStack: Confirm
    LlamaStack-->>Platform: JSON Response
    Platform-->>Client: JSON Response (TLS)

    Note over Client,Cloud: Flow 2: RAG Pipeline (Vector Search + Inference)

    Client->>Platform: POST /v1/agents/run<br/>HTTPS (TLS 1.2+)
    Platform->>LlamaStack: Forward Request<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LlamaStack->>VectorDB: Vector similarity search<br/>HTTP/gRPC<br/>Auth: Token/Password/API Key
    VectorDB-->>LlamaStack: Relevant documents
    LlamaStack->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(with context)<br/>Auth: API Token
    vLLM-->>LlamaStack: Augmented response
    LlamaStack->>PG: Store agent state<br/>SQL 5432/TCP
    PG-->>LlamaStack: Confirm
    LlamaStack-->>Platform: Streaming/JSON Response
    Platform-->>Client: Response (TLS)

    Note over Client,Cloud: Flow 3: Safety-Guarded Inference

    Client->>Platform: POST /v1/inference/chat_completion<br/>HTTPS
    Platform->>LlamaStack: Forward Request<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LlamaStack->>FMS: Safety check (input)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Configurable TLS (FMS_SSL_CERT_PATH)
    FMS-->>LlamaStack: Safety verdict
    alt Input is safe
        LlamaStack->>vLLM: Inference request<br/>Auth: API Token
        vLLM-->>LlamaStack: Model response
        LlamaStack->>FMS: Safety check (output)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        FMS-->>LlamaStack: Safety verdict
        LlamaStack-->>Platform: Response
    else Input blocked
        LlamaStack-->>Platform: Safety violation response
    end
    Platform-->>Client: Final Response (TLS)

    Note over Client,Cloud: Flow 4: Cloud Inference (AWS Bedrock example)

    Client->>Platform: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS
    Platform->>LlamaStack: Forward Request<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LlamaStack->>Cloud: POST inference<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (AWS_BEARER_TOKEN_BEDROCK)
    Cloud-->>LlamaStack: Inference response
    LlamaStack->>PG: Store state<br/>SQL 5432/TCP
    PG-->>LlamaStack: Confirm
    LlamaStack-->>Platform: JSON Response
    Platform-->>Client: Response (TLS)
